OL,3,CUK must prepare for 2C of global
OL,4,Cwarming by 2050, climate advisors warn
OL,6,FThe UK must prepare for a 2C rise in
OL,7,Fglobal temperatures by 2050, according
OL,8,Fto new analysis from the Climate
OL,9,FChange Committee (CCC), commissioned
OL,10,Fby the government.
OL,12,FThe report forecasts that risks from
OL,13,Fheatwaves, droughts, and wildfires
OL,14,Fcould double over the next 25 years,
OL,15,Fwith some peak river flows increasing
OL,16,Fby as much as 40%.
