OL,3,CUK must prepare for 2C of global
OL,4,Cwarming by 2050, climate advisors warn
OL,6,FIt also warns that contingency
OL,7,Fplanning should be in place for a
OL,8,Fworst-case scenario of 4C warming
OL,9,Fabove pre-industrial levels by the end
OL,10,Fof the century.
OL,12,FHowever, this does not necessarily
OL,13,Fmean the goal of limiting global
OL,14,Fwarming to 1.5C is out of reach.
