OL,3,CUK must prepare for 2C of global
OL,4,Cwarming by 2050, climate advisors warn
OL,6,FAccording to Baroness Brown, who leads
OL,7,Fthe CCC's Adaptation Committee: "We
OL,8,Fstill want countries to be driving
OL,9,Ftowards that 1.5 degrees Paris
OL,10,F(Climate) Agreement and getting as
OL,11,Fclose to 1.5 degrees as we can because
OL,12,Fevery fraction of a degree makes a
OL,13,Fdifference and every fraction of a
OL,14,Fdegree makes adaptation more expensive
OL,15,Fas well."
OL,17,FThe new advice follows a critical
OL,18,Fassessment by the CCC earlier this
OL,19,Fyear, which condemned the UK's
OL,20,Finadequate plans for adapting to a
OL,21,Fchanging climate.
