OL,3,CUK must prepare for 2C of global
OL,4,Cwarming by 2050, climate advisors warn
OL,6,FThis could include everything from
OL,7,Fbuilding flood defences and sea walls
OL,8,Fto retrofitting hospitals with air
OL,9,Fconditioning and making train tracks
OL,10,Fmore resilient to changing weather.
OL,12,FThe CCC hopes its advice will support
OL,13,Fthe development of long-term
OL,14,Fgovernment strategies.
OL,16,F"We're at a time when unfortunately,
OL,17,Fthe global commitment to the Paris
OL,18,F(Climate) Agreement is breaking down,"
OL,19,FBaroness Brown told me.
