OL,3,CUK must prepare for 2C of global
OL,4,Cwarming by 2050, climate advisors warn
OL,6,F"Obviously, there is a real worry that
OL,7,Fglobal emission will not reduce at the
OL,8,Flevels that they need to. So
OL,9,Fadaptation will become even more
OL,10,Fcritical so we have to make it work,
OL,11,Fwe've got to find ways to make it
OL,12,Fhappen cost-effectively and we've got
OL,13,Fto be able to find ways."
OL,15,FDr Douglas Parr, chief scientist at
OL,16,FGreenpeace UK, stressed the urgency of
OL,17,Fthe situation, saying: "Alarm bells
OL,18,Fshould be ringing in government.
